Package: bdsreader
Type: Package
Title: Read Data from the Basisdataset Jeugdgezondheidszorg
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Stef", "van Buuren", email = "stef.vanbuuren@tno.nl", role = c("cre", "aut")), 
             person("Arjan", "Huizing", email = "arjan.huizing@tno.nl", role = "aut"))
Description: A light package to read and validate JSON files with
     individual data coded according to the Basisdataset (BDS) 
     Jeugdgezondheidszorg. This version supports fields related to 
     child growth and development.
